    AtlasNode { kind: "C", id: "sim-scale-up-ENERGY-SCALING", raw: "@C sim-scale-up-ENERGY-SCALING :: meta [4!]\n  вҶ’ \"вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ…вҳ… Energy scaling вҖ” KEY FINDING:\"\n  вҶ’ \"\"\n  вҶ’ \"  E(64)   =  845  вҶ’ cells= 64  вҶ’ E/cells = 13.20\"\n  вҶ’ \"  E(512)  = 1507  вҶ’ cells=512  вҶ’ E/cells =  2.94\"\n  вҶ’ \"  E(1024) = 2571  вҶ’ cells=1000 вҶ’ E/cells =  2.57\"\n  вҶ’ \"  E(4096) = 8604  вҶ’ cells=4096 вҶ’ E/cells =  2.10\"\n  вҶ’ \"\"\n  вҶ’ \"  Energy density DECREASES 6.3Г— from ПғВІ=64 to ПғВІ=4096\"\n  вҶ’ \"  log-log fit:  log(E)/log(cells) вҶ’ exponent вүҲ 0.55\"\n  вҶ’ \"  вҶ’ E вҲқ cells^0.55, NOT extensive (would need exponent=1)\"\n  вҶ’ \"\"\n  вҶ’ \"  Interpretation:\"\n  вҶ’ \"  вҳ… ПғВІ=64 toy lattice is in FINITE-SIZE REGIME\"\n  вҶ’ \"  вҳ… Boundary/center init asymmetry (1/(1+dВІ/4)) dominates at L=4\"\n  вҶ’ \"  вҳ… At ПғВІ>=512, energy density approaches plateau ~2.1-2.9\"\n  вҶ’ \"  вҳ… Toy ПғВІ=64 measurements OVERESTIMATE per-cell energy ~5Г—\"", source_file: "atlas.n6", source_line: 49741 },
